---
// Hero Section - Main introduction to RootSpec
---

<section data-test="hero-section" class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span data-test="version-badge" class="version-badge">v7.0.3</span>
    </div>

    <h1 data-test="hero-tagline" class="hero-title">
      Build software where <em>philosophy guides implementation</em>
    </h1>

    <p data-test="hero-explanation" class="hero-description">
      RootSpec is a methodology that transforms product descriptions into testable, hierarchical specifications where <strong>philosophy guides implementation</strong> through a structured five-level approach.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="cta-primary">See How It Works</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec" class="cta-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  padding: var(--space-64) 0 var(--space-48);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-background) 0%, var(--color-surface-elevated) 100%);
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
}

.hero-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--space-16);
}

.hero-badge {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
}

.version-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: white;
  padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-12);
  border-radius: 100px;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.025em;
}

.hero-title {
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
  color: var(--color-text);
}

.hero-title em {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-style: normal;
}

.hero-description {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-32);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-16);
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-primary {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: white;
  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-24);
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: background-color 200ms ease;
  min-width: 140px;
}

.cta-primary:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary-hover);
}

.cta-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--color-text);
  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-24);
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 200ms ease;
  min-width: 140px;
}

.cta-secondary:hover {
  background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-48) 0 var(--space-32);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 280px;
  }
}
</style>